&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/DERBY-6626&quot; title=&quot;Check type of user-supplied modules before creating instances&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;DERBY-6626&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;DERBY-6626&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;: Check type of user-supplied modules before creating instances&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Check explicitly that a custom tool implements the OptionalTool interface.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
